#. [campaign]: id=Pearls_and_Pirates
#: data/campaigns/Of_Pearls_and_Pirates/_main.cfg:42
msgid ""
"A sleepy fishing village on Wesnoth’s west coast finds itself suddenly beset "
"by corsairs. With requests for royal aid falling on deaf ears, the villagers "
"must join forces with the local merfolk and bring the fight to the pirates."
msgstr ""
"Ein verschlafenes Fischerdorf an Wesnoths Westküste sieht sich plötzlich von "
"Korsaren bedrängt. Da Bitten um königliche Hilfe ungehört verhallen, müssen "
"sich die Dorfbewohner mit den örtlichen Angehörigen des Meervolks verbünden "
"und den Kampf zu den Piraten tragen."

#. [campaign]: id=Pearls_and_Pirates
#: data/campaigns/Of_Pearls_and_Pirates/_main.cfg:44
msgid "(Novice level, 5 scenarios.)"
msgstr "(Anfängerniveau, 5 Szenarien.)"

#. [campaign]: id=Pearls_and_Pirates
#. this campaign is not a direct continuation of the story and characters, but is next chronologically and is the recommended next campaign
#: data/campaigns/Of_Pearls_and_Pirates/_main.cfg:48
msgid ""
"The saga continues in\n"
"<i>The Deceiver’s Gambit</i>"
msgstr ""
"Die Saga geht weiter in\n"
"<i>Das Gambit der Lügen</i>"

#. [about]
#: data/campaigns/Of_Pearls_and_Pirates/_main.cfg:52
msgid "Author"
msgstr "Autor"

#. [about]
#: data/campaigns/Of_Pearls_and_Pirates/_main.cfg:58
msgid "Art"
msgstr "Grafik"

#. [message]: speaker=Thea
#: data/campaigns/Of_Pearls_and_Pirates/_main.cfg:116
msgid ""
"I have so much gold! Unless I’m already winning easily, I should make sure "
"to take full advantage of our treasury."
msgstr ""
"Ich habe so viel Gold! Wenn es nicht sowieso nach einem leichten Sieg "
"aussieht, sollte ich darauf achten, unsere Kriegskasse voll auszunutzen."

#. [message]: speaker=Thea
#: data/campaigns/Of_Pearls_and_Pirates/_main.cfg:120
msgid ""
"Many hands make light work, in war as well as peace. Even the most "
"experienced fighter will fall in the face of numbers."
msgstr ""
"Viele Hände machen die Arbeit leicht, im Krieg wie im Frieden. Selbst der "
"erfahrenste Kämpfer fällt gegen eine Übermacht."

#. [message]: speaker=Thea
#: data/campaigns/Of_Pearls_and_Pirates/_main.cfg:135
msgid "No! Not like this..."
msgstr "Nein! Nicht so …"

#. [message]: speaker=Rael
#: data/campaigns/Of_Pearls_and_Pirates/_main.cfg:148
msgid "What will Thea do without me..."
msgstr "Was soll Thea nur ohne mich tun …"

#. [message]: speaker=Elyn
#: data/campaigns/Of_Pearls_and_Pirates/_main.cfg:161
msgid "Argh! I’ve breathed my last!"
msgstr "Argh! Ich hauche mein Leben aus!"

#. [message]: speaker=Diondra
#: data/campaigns/Of_Pearls_and_Pirates/_main.cfg:174
msgid "The depths have taken me..."
msgstr "Die Tiefe hat mich geholt …"

#. [achievement_group]
#: data/campaigns/Of_Pearls_and_Pirates/achievements.cfg:26
msgid "Complete <i>Pirates!</i> without losing any units."
msgstr "Schließt <i>Piraten!</i> ab, ohne Einheiten zu verlieren."

#. [achievement_group]
#: data/campaigns/Of_Pearls_and_Pirates/achievements.cfg:26
